Documentation Standards

---
description: Documentation Standards
globs:
  - "src/**/*.py"
  - "docs/**/*.md"
alwaysApply: true
---

- Use mkdocs for all documentation, with griffe for automatic API references.
- Include docstrings (Google style or reStructuredText) for all modules, classes, and functions.
